Ep7 is out now, and it’s a content challenge! I always say if your happy, healthy and have a properly working bike the content makes itself! It was fun getting out with the remaining contestants and just riding bikes together! Oh and legendary action sports photographer @mason_mashon followed us around for a lap to document it!📸
@pinkbike @pinkbikeacademy #pinkbike #pinkbikeacademy

Ep8 @pinkbikeacademy was a video challenge! I partnered up with @jankyeric to capture each other shredding 1 lap down @bikebigwhite !🤝 we had a blast, go check it out!
@pinkbike @pinkbikeacademy

Episode 9 - The Final Race Pt. 1. Grand prize: $30,000 and a pro mountain biking contract. Today is race day.
Out now on youtube! 
@pinkbike @pinkbikeacademy 
#pinkbike #pinkbikeacademy

I did it! So excited to move forward with @orbea for 2023! This has been an absolute dream to have proper pro contract and salary for MTBing! I’m excited to start this next chapter of my riding career along side OG @geoffgulevich 🤝! I want to continue to push myself and improve my riding all well having the most fun with it and enjoying the process! Thank you so much @pinkbike @pinkbikeacademy @orbea 🙏🙏
As well I wish the best for all the other contestants involved, everyone killed it and it was a blast to spend the week riding with you guys! Massive shout out to @tarppedh , your speed was unmatched, unfortunate they weren’t looking for a racer. I wish the best for you buddy, but I am going to make the most out of this opportunity!🫡😄
📸: @mason_mashon

2022 has been a such fun and exciting year, I’ve had so many good memories and learnt so much through riding! 2023 has presented itself with an amazing opportunity to ride with @orbea bikes and I look forward to it! It’s always tough to say goodbye to the companies that you have grown with and supported you along the way! Thanks so much for the good times @intensecycles @chromagbikes @weareonecomposites @magura_bicycle . I rode a lot of gnarly sh*t and these bikes stood up to everything I could throw at it! It’s been a fun ride, until next time!🥹🤝🍻

Pemby adventures on the Ebike! I would never be caught pedalling in pemberton on a 34C day! This bike changes that.
What’s the point of having a heavier pedal assisted bike to ride to the top if you can’t confidently descend your favourite trails/features? This bike changes that.
The @orbea Wild continues to impress me and puts a smile on my face every time I ride it!😄🥳

So proud of you @birrrelll and everything you went through the last 9 months!❤️ My heart is full!🥹

I miss shredding laps with ya, opening up new lines and trying old gaps! I haven’t met another rider that was as passionate/motivated to progress and try new things. Your skills and confidence was contagious and got me fired up everytime we’d ride! I think it was this lap right after this clip you went and flipped insomnia in the wet!🤯 Keep pushing on the road to recovery @aven.elsberg ❤️‍🩹🙏 #irideforaven

Honoured and hyped to be invited down to ride at the 4th edition of @freeridefiesta ! Thanks @johnysalido and crew for getting the course dialed, looks insane! Can’t wait for some big air, good times and of course plenty of tacos and tequila! See ya in the new year, Jan 14! 🌮🚲🇲🇽🍻 #mtb #fun #mexico

Goodbye Orbea!👋Thanks so much for an amazing opportunity to ride bikes full time this summer @pinkbike @pinkbikeacademy @Orbea! This was a dream come true and a very memorable year! Unfortunately Orbea was not interested in renewing the contract and we will be parting ways in 2024😔! I’m very happy and proud of the year and everything Ive been able accomplished on their bikes! Thanks so much for the support @orbea @ridefoxbike @raceface @shimanomtb @maxxisbike 🍻
Unsure what 2024 will look like, but I know one things for certain, I’ll be back on a DH bike in the park!🤪🫡
#irideforaven #2023 #pinkbike #mtb #freeride #dad
